# smol-cli Shell Aliases

This project uses `smol-cli` тАФ 242 token-efficient shell aliases. Every alias is a standalone command (no prefix).

## File Operations
- `h <file> [n]` тАФ head (first n lines, default 50)
- `t <file> [n]` тАФ tail (last n lines)
- `l <file>` тАФ cat with line numbers
- `sf <pattern>` тАФ find files by name
- `sg <term> [dir]` тАФ recursive grep
- `todo` тАФ find TODO/FIXME/HACK/XXX
- `w <file> <content>` тАФ write to file
- `a <file> <content>` тАФ append to file
- `d <file> -f` тАФ delete (requires -f)
- `cp/mv <src> <dst>` тАФ copy/move
- `mk <dir>` тАФ mkdir -p
- `sr <old> <new> <file>` тАФ search & replace
- `wc <file>` тАФ count lines

## Git
- `gs` тАФ status, `ga` тАФ add all, `gaf <f>` тАФ add file
- `gc <msg>` тАФ commit, `gca <msg>` тАФ commit all
- `gp` тАФ push, `gpf` тАФ force push, `gpl` тАФ pull
- `gd` тАФ diff, `gds` тАФ diff staged
- `gco <b>` тАФ checkout, `gcb <b>` тАФ create branch
- `gl` тАФ log, `glg` тАФ graph log
- `grs <f>` тАФ restore, `gra` тАФ restore all
- `gst` тАФ stash, `gstp` тАФ pop
- `gm <b>` тАФ merge, `grb <b>` тАФ rebase

## Build & Dev (auto-detects package manager)
- `ni` тАФ install, `nid <pkg>` тАФ add dep
- `dev` тАФ dev server, `b` тАФ build
- `lint`/`fix`/`fmt` тАФ lint/autofix/format
- `check` тАФ lint + types + test
- `tu`/`tc` тАФ test/coverage

## Docker & K8s
- `dcu`/`dcd` тАФ compose up/down, `dps` тАФ ps
- `kgp` тАФ get pods, `kl <pod>` тАФ logs

## Rules
- ALWAYS use smol aliases over full commands
- Use `--dry` to preview, `--explain` to describe
- Destructive ops require `--force` or `-f`
